program.description: Liv, Clive and Ravi investigate a fatal car accident and suspect foul play was involved. Starving, Liv and Major consume the brains of the accident victims, a father and his angsty teen daughter. Meanwhile, Clive is questioned about a family that was murdered and is forced to reveal his past history with them; Peyton extends an olive branch to Ravi; and Major hits a road block in his search for Natalie.
